name: com.unity.xr.arkit-face-tracking
description:
Support for face tracking on ARKit.

Includes support for: 
▪ Face pose tracking 
▪ Blendshapes 

Note: Only supported on devices with a forward-facing depth camera, like the iPhone X

_upm.changelog:
### Changed

- Upgraded Apple ARKit Plug-in and AR Subsystems dependency versions from 4.2.8 to 4.2.9.
